    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_1965487725" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1965487725" />
    <a title="Anna" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/41878643-anna"><img alt="Anna" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1488562610p2/41878643.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1965487725?book_show_action=true">Jan 30, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Anna" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Anna" href="/user/show/41878643-anna">Anna</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41878643-anna?shelf=2021">2021</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41878643-anna?shelf=st-paper">st-paper</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41878643-anna?shelf=re-brit">re-brit</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41878643-anna?shelf=a-aw-booker">a-aw-booker</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41878643-anna?shelf=ge-fiction">ge-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41878643-anna?shelf=in-english">in-english</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41878643-anna?shelf=on-shelf-2020">on-shelf-2020</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1965487725" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14346215555495791597">I am not sure what I thought about this book beforehand. I must have had some preconceived notions, because I was stalling. Maybe I was afraid to find only a romance, something disappointing perhaps? <br/>What I did find, was anything but simple, and not really a romance either. More of an opportunity for a mature woman to muse about the worth and price of standing alone, versus finding someone to share her life arrangements with. Adequately packaged in a setting of an of-season hotel in Switzerland,</span>
  <span id="freeText14346215555495791597" style="display:none">I am not sure what I thought about this book beforehand. I must have had some preconceived notions, because I was stalling. Maybe I was afraid to find only a romance, something disappointing perhaps? <br />What I did find, was anything but simple, and not really a romance either. More of an opportunity for a mature woman to muse about the worth and price of standing alone, versus finding someone to share her life arrangements with. Adequately packaged in a setting of an of-season hotel in Switzerland, populated scarcely by an assortment of women, and some peripheral men. Very interesting, and although the world is moving forward and having children and family is not an obvious choice for all the women any more, it is still relevant - what is worth a sacrifice, and what are we willing to compromise, when it comes to how we chose to live our lives, and why?</span>
  <a data-text-id="14346215555495791597" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


